{"tid":1858480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國內蒙新增病例，受感染者住在確診病例樓上","createTime":"2020-02-02T17:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:41:32.000Z","uid":112551,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8af2fbceeb189aa379cc1b22b5dd880a1a266e","tid":1858480,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:35:00.000Z","msg":"【內蒙古1 # 新增病例住在確診病例樓上 #】據內蒙古自治區衛健委通報，2020年2月1日10時至2日10時，#內蒙古新增確診 4例#。確診病例鄂爾多斯市達拉特旗白某，男，40歲，達拉特旗人，<span style=\"color: red;\">居於確診病例宋某樓上</span>，無本市外出史，未接觸過發熱病人，未到過農貿市場，無野生動物接觸史。1月29日，患者自覺胸悶、噁心發熱症狀，31日自駕到達拉特旗人民醫院就診。2月1日，經專家會商，確定為新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎確診病例。<br />\n<br />\nSARS 淘大2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7cc1Uc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7cc1Uc.png&h=37eeabe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42f204b0e81fc19344d33196678de8de267284cc","tid":1858480,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:36:03.000Z","msg":"支爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d808abbe7c0d844f66814d93bc4daa2450bf6e","tid":1858480,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"香港人住得咁密，陷港剷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e360101bc4783d5363e334beaa57a331f9a764d2","tid":1858480,"uid":38293,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ1EGW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ1EGW5.jpg&h=f8522969&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b1e166bb1fac6176de99c57c885eee0f37316c2","tid":1858480,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" c